Package: pqsfinder
Type: Package
Title: Identification of potential quadruplex forming sequences
Version: 0.99.0
Authors@R: c(person("Jiri", "Hon", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                    email = "jiri.hon@gmail.com"),
             person("Matej", "Lexa", role = "ctb",
                    email = "lexa@fi.muni.cz"),
             person("Tomas", "Martinek", role = "ctb",
                    email = "martinto@fit.vutbr.cz"))
Author: Jiri Hon, Matej Lexa and Tomas Martinek
Maintainer: Jiri Hon <jiri.hon@gmail.com>
Description: This package provides functions for identification of potential
    intramolecular quadruplex patterns in DNA sequence.
    The main functionality is to detect the positions of subsequences capable of
    folding into an intramolecular G4-quadruplex.
License: BSD_2_clause + file LICENSE
LazyData: TRUE
Depends:
    Biostrings
Imports:
    Rcpp (>= 0.12.3),
    GenomicRanges,
    IRanges,
    S4Vectors,
    methods
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Suggests: BiocStyle, knitr, Gviz, rtracklayer
LinkingTo: Rcpp, BH, flowCore
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
